(15, 1, '2022-02-15 10:13:53', '2022-02-15 10:13:53', '<strong>Lorem Ipsum</strong> is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry\'s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. It has survived not only five centuries', 'Long Sleeve T-shirt', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'long-sleeve-t-shirt', '', '', '2022-02-15 10:13:55', '2022-02-15 10:13:55', '', 0, 'http://localhost/WordpressSite/?post_type=product&#038;p=15', 0, 'product', '', 0),
